00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:57.000
And I've already told Zhou Zhiyi

00:02:57.760 --> 00:02:58.680
to give both of you

00:02:58.680 --> 00:03:00.320
ten percent shares each

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:02.160
Really?

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:06.040
Ah, Brother Nanfeng, you scared me

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:08.120
I love you

00:03:22.320 --> 00:03:22.840
Back up

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:29.960
Grab the weapons

