Don't untie it

00:04:18.200 --> 00:04:18.960
I'll do it myself

00:04:18.960 --> 00:04:19.760
What are you thinking?

00:04:19.960 --> 00:04:22.560
Wake up, wake up, wake up, wake up

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:34.160
Zheng

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:35.720
Save your strength

00:04:36.520 --> 00:04:37.360
Who are you people

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:40.000
Why did you kidnap us

00:04:40.760 --> 00:04:42.400
Who I am does not matter

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:45.480
But my apprentice Xiao Qian, you got him locked up, right

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:48.200
You are Brother Ming

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.680
You know me

00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:53.600
Tell me, after such a big mess

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:55.400
Should I take your life

00:04:55.760 --> 00:04:57.000
Or do I take your life

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:57.800
Brother Ming

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:00.440
There is no grudge between us

00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:03.480
