This Zheng Nanfeng is so rich

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:29.040
How could I let this chance slip

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:31.120
Boss, you mean

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.320
Does not he have a company too

00:05:43.640 --> 00:05:44.440
How is it going

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:46.240
No news yet

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:48.120
We have searched many places

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:48.920
Could not find them

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:52.440
Where could two living people have gone

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:57.640
Guess how much Zhou Zhiyi

00:05:57.640 --> 00:05:59.240
would pay to ransom you

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:12.000
Hello

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:12.440
Nanfeng

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:13.720
Zheng Nanfeng

00:06:13.960 --> 00:06:16.840
Zhiyi, do not worry, I am fine

00:06:19.200 --> 00:06:20.000
Hello

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:21.960
Zheng Nanfeng is in my hands now

00:06:22.640 --> 00:06:24.720
You know the code of the underworld; do not call the police

00:06:25.800 --> 00:06:27.120
I know, I know

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:28.440
What do you want

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:29.400
You tell me

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:30.480
As for me

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:32.400
I only kidnap, I do not kill

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:34.040
I will give you half a day

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:35.120
Prepare 5 million

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:36.360
5 million

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:38.320
Where am I supposed to find that much money

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.880
I had an Appraiser evaluate you

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:42.240
Your company

00:06:42.400 --> 00:06:43.960
is now worth at least 10 million

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:45.640
I will give you a discount

00:06:45.640 --> 00:06:47.680
5 million in cash, non-sequential notes

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:49.120
Hurry up and get it done

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:50.560
Remember, do not call the police

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:52.560
Otherwise you know the consequences

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.000
Time is too tight

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.240
Give me a bit more time

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:57.800
Hello

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:00.440
He wants 5 million

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:04.400
He even got an Appraiser to evaluate our company

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.240
Looks like it is deeply premeditated

00:07:07.080 --> 00:07:08.080
But in such a short time

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:09.560
