00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:28.240
Then we cannot just sit here now, right

00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:31.040
A Qiang, Xiao Li

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:33.120
Youyou, you stay here and start raising money

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:34.760
We will go find Master Qin

