Xie Rong is a businesswoman

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:43.720
Such rough tactics

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:46.240
I don't think she did it

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:49.240
If you say Xie Jiachang did it,

00:07:49.280 --> 00:07:50.560
I could believe it

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:53.320
But Xie Jiachang is still locked up in prison

00:07:53.320 --> 00:07:54.880
If not Xie Rong, who else could it be?

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:56.320
Master Qin

00:07:56.440 --> 00:07:57.320
No matter what,

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:59.120
You must help us this time

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:00.480
We can't let Nanfeng get hurt

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:02.560
In Haicheng,

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:04.320
Someone with these methods

